Class QNASummaryTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dev.yvgenijsharovskij.n5kanjiandkanjistoryquiz.qna.QNASummaryTable

  • public class QNASummaryTable
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains data for a single row in the QNASummary table. Used to make a list of table rows for easy data handling.
    Also defines the Comparators for table sorting in an inner static class.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Yvgenij Sharovskij
